			</p>

			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4 mt-12 uppercase" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">
				What's the Difference Between Local SEO and National SEO?
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
				<strong class="text-black">Local SEO</strong> focuses on helping your business rank for location-based searches such as:
			</p>
